```plantuml
@startuml
class User {
    String name
    String email
}

class Shelf {
    String name
}

class Note {
    String title
    String body
}

class Article {
    String title
    String url
}

class Tag {
    String body
}

User --> User : followes
User --> Shelf : creates
User --> Note : creates
User --> Article : finds
User --> Tag : followes
User --> Shelf : likes
User --> Note : likes
User --> Article : likes
Shelf o-- Note : contains
Shelf o-- Article : contains
Note *-- Tag : attaches
Article *-- Tag : attaches
Tag --* Shelf : attaches

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle
title netnotes
@enduml
```